"sentence\": \"\\\"Having great kit is extremely important for the athletes, and not just from a technical point of view.\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great kit\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"a technical point\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"view\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You want to look good and you want to feel good in front of your competitors,\\\" said Team SA chef de mission Leon Fleiser.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999998853188637, \"rank\": 1.0511004301026768e-07, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"your competitors\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thanks to our partner Mr Price Sport we have got really good on-field kit and very good off-field kit, and we are extremely happy with what has been launched here tonight.\\\"\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our partner\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Price Sport\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"very good off-field kit\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fleiser said the new design was intended to assist with athlete comfort in the warm conditions expected in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9679489755735853, \"rank\": 0.0326945149304892, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fleiser\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the new design\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete comfort\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"the warm conditions\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Due to the heat in Paris we have made sure we have gone with very lightweight and absorbent materials,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998678645258, \"rank\": 1.3213549710821893e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"very lightweight and absorbent materials\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have got a bit of a different cut as well, to make sure the athletes look good and feel good.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"a different cut\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have also got very good technical kit for them to train in, and we are providing more gym wear for them, for their off-field training, so they have got enough clothes to train in.\\\"\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very good technical kit\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"more gym wear\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"their off-field training\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"enough clothes\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The2024 Olympic Games, to be held between 26 July and 11 Augus